{
  "stem": "7506.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGH] I had to tell his parents, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And him, he was the same age as me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was three months older than me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was born 17 December.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm born the following March.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had to tell them what happened to me, because they said, where's your-- [PAUSES] so I had to tell them my sister, about my mother, about my aunt, my cousin John.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to tell my friend, Jopi's parents, why it was only me arrived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told them, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I also was pleased to tell them that they had told me the morning I arrived in Amsterdam that my mother was indeed alive in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as my [PAUSES] being for the first time with my friend Jopi, [PAUSES] it was like I'd been away, I don't know, somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That he hadn't seen me for a while, which in actual fact was two years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES] [SIGH] I suppose the feeling was, well, we'll just carry on like we did before, as if nothing was different.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing I can remember that he put his arms around me, that he actually physically put his arms around me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, like I said-- obviously, only in Dutch, when he spoke this-- that, you know, he was sorry, what had happened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But basically, that's really all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember that it was much more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then he, too, was only, like, 13, 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES] And to his experience, he had also suffered because of the German occupation, as indeed his father and mother-- no food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, so it was just another side to the suffering, mine to his.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not more, not less at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
